pgTitle: List of former Christian Science churches, societies and buildings

rows.text: First Church of Christ, Scientist (Juneau, Alaska)

101 W 1st St (formerly 1116 N Laura St), Jacksonville
Voluntarily dissolved August 10, 1993 Its former building is now the Jacksonville branch of the Karpeles Manuscript Library Museum
File:Miami FL First Church Christ Scientist01.jpg

Sold in 2012 for $6.25 million. Building will be preserved and reused as a retail space with a 38-story condo tower built above and partially around it. First church now meets in its reading room at 15 West Flagler Street in Miami.
